video.title: Club de Cuervos
video.synopsis: A brother and sister battle high expectations and each other after inheriting a soccer team. A series from the creators of “Nosotros los Nobles.”

episodes.synopsis: When family tragedy strikes, playboy Chava and his workaholic sister Isabel fight over the presidency of their family's professional soccer team.
episodes.title: Be a Captain

episodes.synopsis: While Isabel explores life away from the Cuervos, Chava and Felix scramble to prevent a public relations disaster.
episodes.title: We Make Soap

episodes.synopsis: As Chava tries to make his mark on the team, Isabel looks into Mary Luz's past, and Tony tries to convince Coach Goyo to let him debut.
episodes.title: Uniform Response

episodes.synopsis: Chava battles with Coach Goyo. Meanwhile, Isabel struggles to do business with a sexist sponsor.
episodes.title: Slap

episodes.synopsis: Felix considers an offer from a rival team, Chava tries to impress a cute reporter, and Isabel makes a new friend.
episodes.title: Barriers to Exit

episodes.synopsis: While the players anxiously prepare for the most important game of the season, Rafael reflects on his upcoming retirement.
episodes.title: Lucky to Play

episodes.synopsis: Felix carefully maps out his plans for the team's lineup next season, but Chava has ideas of his own.
episodes.title: Our Guggenheim

episodes.synopsis: A documentary profile offers a behind-the-scenes look at European superstar Aitor Cardone's arrival to the Cuervos.
episodes.title: Aitor

episodes.synopsis: As Chava rides the wave of Aitor's fame, Moises begins feeling insecure about his place on the team. Isabel deals with the fallout from her interview.
episodes.title: Spanish Fever

episodes.synopsis: Aitor's presence upsets the balance of the team, Isabel struggles with being ostracized, and Potro's jealousy continues to create problems.
episodes.title: New Dick in Town

episodes.synopsis: Felix is left to manage the team on his own while a new arrival keeps Chava busy.
episodes.title: Push

episodes.synopsis: Chava has the worst birthday ever as scandal engulfs Aitor and Isabel seizes an opportunity.
episodes.title: Happy Birthday Mr. President

episodes.synopsis: Chava and Isabel's rivalry comes to a head as the team faces its greatest challenge and Mary Luz asserts herself.
episodes.title: Iglesias vs. Iglesias

episodes.synopsis: Chava's family worries about where he could be, while Isabel faces unexpected challenges with the team's division status.
episodes.title: Descenso

episodes.synopsis: When cash flow problems plague the Cuervos, the players revolt. Isabel makes a serious personal decision. Hugo Sanchez searches for Chava.
episodes.title: Welcome to Second

episodes.synopsis: Chava locks himself in Aitor's apartment for 70 days. When he finally emerges, a drug-fueled revelation has him questioning his entire identity.
episodes.title: Who Are You Looking For?

episodes.synopsis: Chava returns and is focused on reconciliation. Isabel is skeptical but must focus on a lawsuit, unmotivated players and emotional struggles.
episodes.title: Ho Oponopono

episodes.synopsis: A traitor works to undermine the Cuervos in the playoffs. Rafael and Isabel’s professional arguments impact their marriage.
episodes.title: Matahari

episodes.synopsis: A new coach shakes things up for the team. Isabel confronts Chava, who retaliates by calling immigration services on Potro.
episodes.title: The Oasis in the Desert

episodes.synopsis: Isabel gains fans of her own as Cuervos continues to win. A jealous Chava throws himself into developing a casino deal.
episodes.title: La Salvadora

episodes.synopsis: Mary Luz and Chava try to convince the wild and wealthy Ricky Lamas to invest in their casino. Mary Luz encounters someone from her past.
episodes.title: The Truce

episodes.synopsis: Isabel tries to convince her team there is no curse. Chava investigates Mary Luz's history. Potro's fake marriage is not what he expected.
episodes.title: The Curse of the Black Feather

episodes.synopsis: The Cuervos and Carneros face off in the championship game to see who will ascend to Division 1. Chava makes an unexpected power play.
episodes.title: Iglesias vs Iglesias 2

episodes.synopsis: Isabel and Chava adjust to life as co-presidents of the Cuervos team and take on the governor as their first obstacle.
episodes.title: The Third Generation

episodes.synopsis: When the Cuervos bring a new high-profile teammate on board, Rafa must clean up a mess caused by Chava and Isabel.
episodes.title: The Treaty of Versailles 14

episodes.synopsis: Isabel's decision puts a strain on the Cuervos team lineup just as the draft begins, and they must scramble to recover.
episodes.title: The Leftovers

episodes.synopsis: Chava's gubernatorial candidacy hits a snag when old incriminating photos of him surface. Isabel mixes business with pleasure.
episodes.title: Business or Pleasure?

episodes.synopsis: Chava's relationship with Isabel Cantú ends up benefitting the Cuervos financially, while creating a challenge for his sister.
episodes.title: The Road Back

episodes.synopsis: The siblings fight over whether to fire Cuau. Chava gets nervous filming his first campaign ad for governor.
episodes.title: Our Cuau

episodes.synopsis: Rafa is interviewed about his career. Chava thinks he’s a better political candidate when he improvises -- until an angry moment is caught on TV.
episodes.title: Church and State

episodes.synopsis: The team struggles to keep key player Moisés happy after a disappointing commercial. Cuau is offered a chance to enter the political arena.
episodes.title: Puebla…

episodes.synopsis: Chava makes a big decision regarding his campaign and personal life. Isabel receives a shocking and revealing email not intended for her.
episodes.title: Girl, Interrupted

episodes.synopsis: A reporter makes a troubling discovery about Don Salvador Iglesias and his past. Isabel and Chava turn to their mothers for clarity on their father.
episodes.title: The Heart of Nuevo Toledo

episodes.synopsis: Amid hostility from the public about his father, Chava ponders a name change. The Iglesias family debate selling the Cuervos to pay off their debt.
episodes.title: Diego Villalobos

episodes.synopsis: When Gaspar steals players from the Cuervos, Isabel seeks help from unlikely sources. Chava's plan to raise money is foiled by a person from his past.
episodes.title: You've Got Email

episodes.synopsis: Potro helps Isabel block Fede's romantic advances. Chava launches Cuervos TV. Emaíl's religion causes conflict with Aitor. Gaspar's sabotage continues.
episodes.title: Valle de Silicon

episodes.synopsis: Mary Luz enters World Cup negotiations. Chava gets creative when the Cuervos are moved to a 7 a.m. time slot. Isabel and Fede's tryst hits the press.
episodes.title: The Slut of Nuevo Toledo

episodes.synopsis: Isabel secretly helps Potro improve his coaching. Fed up with all the bad press about the team, Chava decides they should use it to their advantage.
episodes.title: Cyrano de Bergerac

episodes.synopsis: Chava urges Isabel to lean in to her "promiscuous" reputation. Emaíl worries he's been found out. The Cuervos get a new coach and face the Tarántulas.
episodes.title: The Black Plague

episodes.synopsis: When the Iglesias bank accounts are frozen, the players leverage social media to raise money, but their lack of focus affects a qualifying match.
episodes.title: Four Minor Miracles

episodes.synopsis: The Cuervos go on a retreat to unplug from social media, but Isabel and Rafa's feud and a confession from Emaíl threaten the team-building dynamic.
episodes.title: Concentration Camp

episodes.synopsis: Paty and Chava produce a documentary that could change the course of fate for the Cuervos. Mary Luz charms Maldonado to help take down Gaspar.
episodes.title: Something About Mary Luz

episodes.synopsis: Traveling together to the semifinals, Isabel and Rafa are "Two for the Road," reflecting on their first meeting in 2006 and their decade-long marriage.
episodes.title: Two for the Road

episodes.synopsis: After Chava kidnaps a reporter, his family asks him to do the unthinkable. Gaspar calls the authorities on Mary Luz. The Cuervos play in the semifinals.
episodes.title: A Trip to the Moon

episodes.synopsis: As the finals arrive, the Cuervos and Nuevo Toledo are on the brink of ruin. Chava and Isabel must pull off their greatest scheme yet to save them.
episodes.title: Todos Somos Cuervos
